During the exit conference, the Management asked for indulgence and said that they permitted to implement the recommendations prospectively. They assured the Audit Team that these deficiencies will no longer be repeated as they were only unintentionally committed rooted by their desire to quickly safeguard and meet the needs of their constituents during the heat of the pandemic.

