While we recognize the ongoing efforts of the municipality, we have recommended that in order to enjoy the benefits of effective Ecological Solid Waste Management and to avoid possible sanctions, the members of the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board:
 Facilitate any revision of the SWMP;
 Establish material recovery facilities in the barangays;
 Initiate for the eventual conversion from controlled dumpsite into sanitary landfill;
 Enforce waste segregation at source; and
Monitor and encourage utmost compliance by its component barangays.

We have recommended that in order to enjoy the benefits of effective Ecological Solid Waste Management and to avoid possible sanctions, the members of the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board:
Facilitate any revision of the SWMP;
Establish material recovery facilities in the barangays;
Initiate for the eventual conversion from controlled dumpsite into sanitary landfill;
Enforce waste segregation at source; and
Monitor and encourage utmost compliance by its component barangays.

We have recommended that in order to validate the existence, reliability and accuracy, custody and status of agency assets as well as to establish proper valuation, sufficient control and accountability for each property, Management evaluate the workloads of personnel and ensure that:

The members of the Inventory Committee conduct annual physical inventory and thereafter  prepare and submit the RPCPPE for adjustment in the agency books/records, if necessary;
Personnel assigned at the Treasury Office maintain Property Cards and keep inventory records updated;
The Accounting personnel maintain the PPE Ledger cards and regularly reconcile the same with the inventory records maintained by the Treasury Office.

While we recognize the ongoing efforts of the municipality, we recommended that in order to enjoy the benefits of effective Ecological Solid Waste Management and to avoid possible sanctions, the members of the Municipal Solid Waste Management Board:

•	Facilitate any revision of the SWMP;
•	Establish material recovery facilities on barangays  
•	Initiate for the eventual conversion from controlled dumpsite into sanitary landfill; 
•	Enforce waste segregation at source; and 
•	Monitor  and encourage utmost compliance by its component barangays.
